snippet.title: Kevin Hart, Wesley Snipes Talk ‘True Story’
snippet.description:
Comedian Kevin Hart discusses how much of his new Netflix series “True Story” is based on his real life. Plus, Hart’s co-star Wesley Snipes talks working with the stand-up comedian and shares how he feels about Mahershala Ali starring in the upcoming “Blade” film. 
#KevinHart #WesleySnipes #MahershalaAli
